<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī śakavaruṣaṁbulu 
<lb n="2"/>1213 Agu nēṁṭi kharasaṁvatsa 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ra kārttika śuddha 15 gu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti śrī 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>manmahāmaṁḍaḷēśvara kākatiyya 
<lb n="5"/>kumāra ru<unclear>ddra</unclear>dēva mahārājulaku 
<lb n="6"/>puṁṇyamu gānu rāyasakalasēnādhi 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>pati sōmayādula ru<unclear>ddra</unclear>dēvaniṁgā 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ru juvulakaṁṭi mūlasthānaṁ bhīmanā 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>thadēvaraku Ācaṁdrārkkasthāyigānu 
<lb n="10"/>[I]ccina vritti<unclear>rē</unclear>gaḍa kha 2 maṁgaḷamahāśrī 
<lb n="11"/>svadattaṁ paradattaṁ vā yō 
<lb n="12"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> rvvarṣasa 
<lb n="13"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> yāṁ jāya 
